name: NoteAble
body: ### Improve your note recognition abilities NoteAble is a simple, interactive, ear training utility designed to help you learn how to recognize notes. NoteAble is catered to those learning guitar but it can also great for anyone looking to train their ear! You can download NoteAble today for Android on Google Play for free! ### Contact Marco Suson GitHub: [@msuson](https://github.com/msuson) email: masuson117@gmail.com
